note: 2017-07-31 - streamer example STREAMER log. Sender sends one 2Mb message
Streamer chunks incoming data into a 250Kb buffer and stops issuing flows to sender when buffer is full.
Streamer sends 250Kb to receiver and then sends flow to sender.
Until sender gets flow it has no session window to send to streamer and holds data in sender buffers
address_receive: end of message = true; wake = true
